OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FThe King's "high stakes" visit to the
OL,7,FUS this week was high risk but also a
OL,8,F"phenomenal opportunity", according to
OL,9,Fsenior palace staff, as they reflect
OL,10,Fon perhaps the biggest week of Charles
OL,11,FIII's reign so far.
OL,13,FBuckingham Palace says the face-to-
OL,14,Fface meetings with Donald Trump were a
OL,15,Fchance for the most senior royals to
OL,16,Fshowcase the depth of the
OL,17,Ftransatlantic relationship without the
OL,18,F"noise" of recent events.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@XO]pD@AOUpD@XO]zD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
