CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla arrived
OL,7,Fin Washington on Monday with the US-UK
OL,8,Frelationship under severe strain
OL,9,Ffollowing the war in Iran.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FBut they left the US on good terms
OL,17,Fwith Trump and the first lady, and
OL,18,Ftheir departure was followed by a
OL,19,Fboost to the Scottish whisky industry
OL,20,Fwhen the president lifted tariffs on
OL,21,Fimports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FThe King's speech to Congress, only
OL,7,Fthe second time in history that a
OL,8,FBritish monarch has been invited to
OL,9,Faddress US lawmakers, pushed back on
OL,10,Fmany of the criticisms Donald Trump
OL,11,Fhad levelled at the UK in the recent
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FBut it was decided the King had the
OL,15,Fauthority, experience, and enough
OL,16,Fgoodwill with the president to deliver
OL,17,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,F"It was a high stakes address to
OL,7,FCongress," said a palace source
OL,8,Finvolved in the speech. "It's a
OL,9,Fmeasure of how much he personally
OL,10,Fcares" about the relationship with the
OL,11,FUS, they said.
OL,13,FOne palace official added: "What
OL,14,Flooked like risk and challenge was
OL,15,Falso a phenomenal opportunity. One
OL,16,Fthat was grasped in both hands by the
OL,17,FKing and we shall leave you to
OL,18,Fconclude what the outcome of that was."
OL,26,@oD@JO]rD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FThe King's speech did achieve what no
OL,7,FUS politician has managed in recent
OL,8,Fyears - to get divided House of
OL,9,FRepresentatives and the Senate to come
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,FAs the US marks the 250th anniversary
OL,13,Fof ejecting a British monarch after
OL,14,Fthe War of Independence, it seemed
OL,15,Fmost of Washington's political elite
OL,16,Fwas happy to welcome one back with
OL,17,Fopen arms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FGiven the significant anniversary, a
OL,7,Fsenior palace source said: "The word
OL,8,Fhistoric is much overused and we
OL,9,Falways hesitate to use it in the
OL,10,Fpalace, but I think one could use that
OL,11,Fterm for this visit."
OL,13,FITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,14,Freflects on the final day of the King
OL,15,Fand Queen's state visit to the US
OL,17,FGeorge III, who was the last King of
OL,18,FAmerica, is King Charles' five-time
OL,19,Fgreat grandfather.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FAnd Charles reassured Congress he
OL,7,Fhadn't come to the US as part of some
OL,8,F"rear-guard action".
OL,10,FBut he did deliver some hard-hitting
OL,11,Fmessages on issues like Ukraine, Nato,
OL,12,FAfghanistan, defence spending, melting
OL,13,Fice caps, checks on executive power,
OL,14,Fand the need to reject the "clarion
OL,15,Fcalls for nationalism", which felt
OL,16,Fvery much like a criticism of Trump's
OL,17,FMaga movement.
OL,19,FSo why did they allow King Charles to
OL,20,Fdeliver such a punchy speech?
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]vD@\OUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FA source who helped craft it with the
OL,7,FKing and the government said: "First,
OL,8,Fwhat the King says will always be
OL,9,Fguided by the truth.
OL,11,F"Two, it will be guided by conscience.
OL,12,FAnd three, they're all observable
OL,13,Ffacts. Everything that is in that
OL,14,Fspeech is an observable fact. And so,
OL,15,FI think we felt very comfortable with
OL,16,Fthe King speaking as he did."
OL,26,@oD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FAfter a tense few months for Prime
OL,7,FMinister Keir Starmer, who's been on
OL,8,Fthe receiving end of Trump's many
OL,9,Ftongue lashings about the UK, the
OL,10,Fpalace was keen to point out the King
OL,11,Fhad not been sent to the US simply to
OL,12,Frepair the relationship.
OL,14,F"I wouldn't say we were there to
OL,15,Fchange the relationship", said a
OL,16,Fsenior member of the King's team, but
OL,17,Fthey acknowledged the Windsors and the
OL,18,FTrumps did get on very well.
OL,26,@wD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FThey said: "It's not a competition
OL,7,Fbetween the King and the government.
OL,8,FThe King is there to support the
OL,9,Fgovernment, to help the government.
OL,11,F"It was at the government's request,
OL,12,Fof course, that he undertook this
OL,13,Fvisit. And the King and the Queen have
OL,14,Fbeen able to help the government in
OL,15,Fany way and to get the relationship
OL,16,Fperhaps more widely understood by a
OL,17,Fwider number of people without some of
OL,18,Fthe noise of current affairs."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FAs for how the King and Queen got on
OL,7,Fwith the Trumps, royal sources said
OL,8,Fthe relationship was as friendly in
OL,9,Fprivate as it appeared to be in
OL,10,Fpublic, however "unlikely" that might
OL,11,Fseem.
OL,13,F"They get on very well", a senior
OL,14,Fsource said who was closely involved
OL,15,Fin the visit, and it was not just the
OL,16,Ftwo heads of state.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@ZO]uD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,F"It's all four of them with each
OL,7,Fother. The Queen and the president.
OL,8,FThe Queen and the first lady. The King
OL,9,Fand the first lady. The King and the
OL,10,Fpresident. It's a pairing, sort of
OL,11,Funlikely though it might be in many
OL,12,Fways," they said.
OL,14,F"The warmth that you see in public is
OL,15,Fabsolutely the warmth you see in
OL,16,Fprivate. That meeting in the Oval
OL,17,FOffice? There was an awful lot of
OL,18,Fwarmth and laughter", said a senior
OL,19,Fmember of the King's staff.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FKing Charles did not allow himself a
OL,7,Fmoment of satisfaction after leaving
OL,8,Fthe US at the end of the four-day
OL,9,Fvisit.
OL,11,FHe'd already opened his red boxes
OL,12,Fmoments after take-off and was working
OL,13,Fon his briefing notes for his
OL,14,Fsubsequent visit to Bermuda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31014
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,F"He's not a man to dwell long on what
OL,7,Fsome may consider yesterday's
OL,8,Fsuccesses, he is always looking
OL,9,Ftowards tomorrow's opportunities, so
OL,10,Fgenerally we've tried to encourage him
OL,11,Fto feel positive - and he has, about
OL,12,Fthe way that the American leg has gone
OL,13,Fin particular."
OL,15,FThe palace's aim for the state visit
OL,16,Fwas to move the dial in the US-UK
OL,17,Frelationship and even a marginal
OL,18,Fimprovement would have been considered
OL,19,Fa success.
OL,26,@uD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31015
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777856582
OL,3,CKing's 'high stakes' visit to the US
OL,4,Cwas a risk that's been rewarded
OL,6,FHowever, the palace source added: "We
OL,7,Fwill sit on the plane and think that
OL,8,Fwas a week well spent."
OL,10,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,11,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,12,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,13,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
